text.tspan: Same as last night but Cirno and Youmu will appear now.
Cirno spawns in her room (cam ⑨) and makes her way to your room through
either hall. She can't be stopped by the flash, but makes a distinct sound when
she enters your room. Once she's in, a ⑨ button will appear in her room. Click
it to send her back to her room.
Youmu behaves similarly to Reimu and Marisa, but can attack through either
hall. She can flip-flop between them at a moment's notice, so listen carefully to
know when she does so. Use your flash to scare her away.
